p://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"PHOTO\", \"from\": 356, \"to\": 361}, {\"ngram\": \"EPA-EFE PublishedSep\", \"from\": 363, \"to\": 383}, {\"ngram\": \"UpdatedSep\", \"from\": 403, \"to\": 413}, {\"ngram\": \"another\", \"from\": 576, \"to\": 583}, {\"ngram\": \"AFP\", \"from\": 589, \"to\": 592}, {\"ngram\": \"spades\", \"from\": 610, \"to\": 616}, {\"ngram\": \"the thing\", \"from\": 618, \"to\": 627}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 633, \"to\": 639}, {\"ngram\": \"sport - emotion\", \"from\": 658, \"to\": 673}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mainly packed stadia, iconic venues and the feel-good factor derived from the earlier Olympics turned the Paralympics into a festival of sport, according to Michael Payne, the IOC's former head of marketing.\", \"from\": 680, \"to\": 887, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 837, \"end\": 850, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Payne_(executive)\", \"score\": 0.9998432523751143, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Michael Payne\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Payne_(executive)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Payne_(executive)\"}, {\"begin\": 856, \"end\": 859, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.588676432160742e-25, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mainly packed stadia\", \"from\": 680, \"to\": 700}, {\"ngram\": \"iconic venues\", \"from\": 702, \"to\": 715}, {\"ngram\": \"the feel-good factor\", \"from\": 720, \"to\": 740}, {\"ngram\": \"the earlier Olympics\", \"from\": 754, \"to\": 774}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paralympics\", \"from\": 782, \"to\": 797}, {\"ngram\": \"a festival\", \"from\": 803, \"to\": 813}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 817, \"to\": 822}, {\"ngram\": \"marketing\", \"from\": 877, \"to\": 886}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Its counterpart, the International Paralympic Committee, can breathe a sigh of relief after Rio de Janeiro was widely criticised for its hosting in 2016 and the Tokyo edition was deprived of spectators because of Covid-19 restrictions.\", \"from\": 889, \"to\": 1124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 910, \"end\": 944, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Paralympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Paralympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Paralympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Paralympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 981, \"end\": 995, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.28263173107108e-15, \"text\": \"Rio de Janeiro\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\"}, {\"begin\": 1050, \"end\": 1055, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.88719332891314e-16, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Its counterpart\", \"from\": 889, \"to\": 904}, {\"ngram\": \"a sigh\", \"from\": 958, \"to\": 964}, {\"ngram\": \"relief\", \"from\": 968, \"to\": 974}, {\"ngram\": \"its hosting\", \"from\": 1022, \"to\": 1033}, {\"ngram\": \"spectators\", \"from\": 1080, \"to\": 1090}, {\"ngram\": \"Covid-19 restrictions\", \"from\": 1102, \"to\": 1123}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Paris built on the magic of the Olympic Games and delivered a spectacular Paralympic Games - to my mind the greatest ever,\\\" said Payne.\", \"from\": 1126, \"to\": 1262, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1127, \"end\": 1132, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999781721, \"rank\": 2.1922478260777072e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the magic\", \"from\": 1142, \"to\": 1151}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1155, \"to\": 1172}, {\"ngram\": \"a spectacular Paralympic Games\", \"from\": 1187, \"to\": 1217}, {\"ngram\": \"my mind\", \"from\": 1223, \"to\": 1230}, {\"ngram\": \"Payne\", \"from\": 1256, \"to\": 1261}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"All the ingredients that made the Olympics so special have been carried forward to the Paras, delivering an incredible atmosphere.\\\"\", \"from\": 1264, \"to\": 1396, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"All the ingredients\", \"from\": 1265, \"to\": 1284}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1295, \"to\": 1307}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paras\", \"from\": 1348, \"to\": 1357}, {\"ngram\": \"an incredible atmosphere\", \"from\": 1370, \"to\": 1394}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Another former IOC marketing executive, Terrence Burns, said in his 30-plus years of Paralympics, there was no comparison \\\"in both fan and commercial interest\\\".\", \"from\": 1398, \"to\": 1559, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1413, \"end\": 1416, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.588676432160742e-25, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Terrence Burns\", \"from\": 1438, \"to\": 1452}, {\"ngram\": \"his 30-plus years\", \"from\": 1462, \"to\": 1479}, {\"ngram\": \"Paralympics\", \"from\": 1483, \"to\": 1494}, {\"ngram\": \"no comparison\", \"from\": 1506, \"to\": 1519}, {\"ngram\": \"both fan and commercial interest\", \"from\": 1524, \"to\": 1556}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In so many ways, I believe the Paralympics are truly coming into their own as a separate yet complementary 'product' from the Olympics,\\\" Burns said.\", \"from\": 1561, \"to\": 1710, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so many ways\", \"from\": 1565, \"to\": 1577}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paralympics\", \"from\": 1589, \"to\": 1604}, {\"ngram\": \"a separate yet complementary 'product\", \"from\": 1640, \"to\": 1677}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1684, \"to\": 1696}, {\"ngram\": \"Burns\", \"from\": 1699, \"to\": 1704}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I give the IOC full marks for working hard to make the Paralympics a product that brands want not only to support, but to market.\", \"from\": 1712, \"to\": 1842, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the IOC\", \"from\": 1720, \"to\": 1727}, {\"ngram\": \"full marks\", \"from\": 1728, \"to\": 1738}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paralympics\", \"from\": 1764, \"to\": 1779}, {\"ngram\": \"brands\", \"from\": 1795, \"to\": 1801}, {\"ngram\": \"market\", \"from\": 1835, \"to\": 1841}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"(It is) a difference with a profound distinction.\\\"\", \"from\": 1844, \"to\": 1895, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a difference\", \"from\": 1853, \"to\": 1865}, {\"ngram\": \"a profound distinction\", \"from\": 1871, \"to\": 1893}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For Payne, who in nearly two decades at the IOC was credited with modernising the organisation's brand and improving its finances through sponsorship, the high profile of the Paralympics had hugely positive ramifications.\", \"from\": 1897, \"to\": 2118, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1941, \"end\": 1944, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.588676432160742e-25, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Payne\", \"from\": 1901, \"to\": 1906}, {\"ngram\": \"nearly two decades\", \"from\": 1915, \"to\": 1933}, {\"ngram\": \"the organisation's brand\", \"from\": 1975, \"to\": 1999}, {\"ngram\": \"its finances\", \"from\": 2014, \"to\": 2026}, {\"ngram\": \"sponsorship\", \"from\": 2035, \"to\": 2046}, {\"ngram\": \"the high profile\", \"from\": 2048, \"to\": 2064}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paralympics\", \"from\": 2068, \"to\": 2083}, {\"ngram\": \"hugely positive ramifications\", \"from\": 2088, \"to\": 2117}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Paralympics provides a massive boost worldwide to the disabled movement - bringing the issue of disability front and centre,\\\" said the Irishman.\", \"from\": 2120, \"to\": 2270, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Paralympics\", \"from\": 2121, \"to\": 2136}, {\"ngram\": \"a massive boost\", \"from\": 2146, \"to\": 2161}, {\"ngram\": \"the disabled movement\", \"from\": 2175, \"to\": 2196}, {\"ngram\": \"the issue\", \"from\": 2208, \"to\": 2217}, {\"ngram\": \"disability front\", \"from\": 2221, \"to\": 2237}, {\"ngram\": \"centre\", \"from\": 2242, \"to\": 2248}, {\"ngram\": \"the Irishman\", \"from\": 2256, \"to\": 2268}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"(There is) a real legacy from general accessibility to a broader debate and awareness about disability throughout society.\\\"\", \"from\": 2272, \"to\": 2396, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a real legacy\", \"from\": 2284, \"to\": 2297}, {\"ngram\": \"general accessibility\", \"from\": 2303, \"to\": 2324}, {\"ngram\": \"a broader debate\", \"from\": 2328, \"to\": 2344}, {\"ngram\": \"awareness\", \"from\": 2349, \"to\": 2358}, {\"ngram\": \"disability\", \"from\": 2365, \"to\": 2375}, {\"ngram\": \"society\", \"from\": 2387, \"to\": 2394}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He said that before the Paralympic Games became mainstream, \\\"disability was often hidden and rarely talked about\\\".\", \"from\": 2398, \"to\": 2512, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Paralympic Games\", \"from\": 2418, \"to\": 2438}, {\"ngram\": \"disability\", \"from\": 2459, \"to\": 2469}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Payne said the athletes were the main actors in making the Paralympics the spectacle they are, with a knock-on positive impact for disabled people back in their own countries.\", \"from\": 2514, \"to\": 2689, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Payne\", \"from\": 2514, \"to\": 2519}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 2525, \"to\": 2537}, {\"ngram\": \"the main actors\", \"from\": 2543, \"to\": 2558}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paralympics\", \"from\": 2569, \"to\": 2584}, {\"ngram\": \"the spectacle\", \"from\": 2585, \"to\": 2598}, {\"ngram\": \"a knock-on positive impact\", \"from\": 2614, \"to\": 2640}, {\"ngram\": \"disabled people\", \"from\": 2645, \"to\": 2660}, {\"ngram\": \"their own countries\", \"from\": 2669, \"to\": 2688}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The stories of what some refer to as 'the super humans' provides an inspirational platform that is impossible to ignore,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2691, \"to\": 2822, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the super humans\", \"from\": 2730, \"to\": 2746}, {\"ngram\": \"an inspirational platform\", \"from\": 2757, \"to\": 2782}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Everyone recognises the incredible challenges that each Paralympic athlete has had to overcome - and watching their performances in Paris, you look on totally awestruck.\\\"\", \"from\": 2824, \"to\": 2995, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2881, \"end\": 2899, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Para-athletics\", \"score\": 0.9999998355688284, \"rank\": 1.6443114953026426e-07, \"text\": \"Paralympic athlete\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Para-athletics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Para-athletics\"}, {\"begin\": 2957, \"end\": 2962, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999781721, \"rank\": 2.1922478260777072e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Everyone\", \"from\": 2825, \"to\": 2833}, {\"ngram\": \"the incredible challenges\", \"from\": 2845, \"to\": 2870}, {\"ngram\": \"their performances\", \"from\": 2935, \"to\": 2953}, {\"ngram\": \"totally awestruck\", \"from\": 2976, \"to\": 2993}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Burns also said the athletes drove the narrative.\", \"from\": 2997, \"to\": 3046, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Burns\", \"from\": 2997, \"to\": 3002}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 3013, \"to\": 3025}, {\"ngram\": \"the narrative\", \"from\": 3032, \"to\": 3045}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think people react and relate to sport through a single prism: emotion,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 3048, \"to\": 3132, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3057, \"to\": 3063}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 3084, \"to\": 3089}, {\"ngram\": \"a single prism\", \"from\": 3098, \"to\": 3112}, {\"ngram\": \"emotion\", \"from\": 3114, \"to\": 3121}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Paras deliver on that in spades.\", \"from\": 3134, \"to\": 3171, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3135, \"end\": 3144, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Paras\", \"score\": 0.9999999999395186, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Paras\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Paras\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Paras\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"spades\", \"from\": 3164, \"to\": 3170}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Increased coverage and exposure means more fans can experience it.\\\"\", \"from\": 3172, \"to\": 3239, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Increased coverage\", \"from\": 3172, \"to\": 3190}, {\"ngram\": \"exposure\", \"from\": 3195, \"to\": 3203}, {\"ngram\": \"more fans\", \"from\": 3210, \"to\": 3219}]}, {\"sentence\": \"British amputee sprinter Jonnie Peacock is one who would like that exposure to be even greater.\", \"from\": 3241, \"to\": 3336, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3241, \"end\": 3248, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9998827972515775, \"rank\": 0.00010042174737118117, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 3266, \"end\": 3280, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonnie_Peacock\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jonnie Peacock\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonnie_Peacock\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonnie_Peacock\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that exposure\", \"from\": 3303, \"to\": 3316}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The two-time 100m champion made an impassioned plea to World Athletics that Paralympic athletes be included in the main televised section of the elite Diamond League meetings.\", \"from\": 3338, \"to\": 3513, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3393, \"end\": 3408, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 6.683941845259135e-13, \"text\": \"World Athletics\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics\"}, {\"begin\": 3489, \"end\": 3503, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diamond_League\", \"score\": 0.9999747149517891, \"rank\": 2.528484397245789e-05, \"text\": \"Diamond League\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resour