gram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3830, \"to\": 3842}, {\"ngram\": \"my mind\", \"from\": 3861, \"to\": 3868}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Both events are now so big, they each need their own stage... and frankly I think Paralympics are better served on the stage by themselves.\\\"\", \"from\": 3871, \"to\": 4012, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Both events\", \"from\": 3872, \"to\": 3883}, {\"ngram\": \"their own stage\", \"from\": 3915, \"to\": 3930}, {\"ngram\": \"Paralympics\", \"from\": 3954, \"to\": 3965}, {\"ngram\": \"the stage\", \"from\": 3987, \"to\": 3996}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Burns, who since leaving the IOC has assisted five successful Olympic bid city campaigns, says Peacock does have a point.\", \"from\": 4014, \"to\": 4135, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4043, \"end\": 4046, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.588676432160742e-25, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 4109, \"end\": 4116, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"score\": 0.9999999155825243, \"rank\": 8.440646546852329e-08, \"text\": \"Peacock\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Burns\", \"from\": 4014, \"to\": 4019}, {\"ngram\": \"five successful Olympic bid city campaigns\", \"from\": 4060, \"to\": 4102}, {\"ngram\": \"a point\", \"from\": 4127, \"to\": 4134}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I would also argue that mixing might dilute the focus on Paralympic sport, though (it is) worth experimenting with.\\\"\", \"from\": 4137, \"to\": 4254, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4195, \"end\": 4211, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paralympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 7.6256